        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help Extend Auditory Relief Act of 2025 or the HEAR Act of 2025&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill provides for Medicare coverage of hearing aids and hearing rehabilitation services. Covered services include hearing aid assessments, fittings, and related instructional services.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
